div.p: unexported context key type type correlationKey struct{} Prevents collisions with other packages. Stored via context.WithValue(ctx, correlationKey{}, id). Retrieved via ctx.Value(correlationKey{}).(string).

NO fmt.Println in handlers NO fmt.Printf in consumer loops NO log.Print (stdlib log package) ALL output through *slog.Logger Every log line is valid JSON on stdout correlation_id propagated via context
